{"tid":970792,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【人多勢弱】無綫百萬行被ViuTV MIRROR搶風頭 樂易玲有意組隊撼MIRROR","createTime":"2019-01-06T06:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T13:32:16.000Z","uid":164435,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a0399c96089e6d905c184d8b8e85ebe2b20daf88","tid":970792,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"無綫由高層樂易玲、鄭善強、杜之克率領近六十藝員現身，喺中環參與百萬行，雖然人多，但明顯勢弱，人氣未如過往熱鬧，為人熟悉嘅藝員只得陳煒、黎諾懿、徐榮及陳庭欣等，對此樂小姐話：「好多藝人要開工，而且今次場地同之前唔同，唔可以容納咁多人，今日藝人連工作人員都有約90人。」面對ViuTV新組合MIRROR人氣勁搶盡風頭，樂小姐話：「都有留意望下，覺得幾好幾靚仔。」有冇意撬佢哋過檔？樂小姐話：「唔好咁。」提到無綫可以組隊撼過，樂小姐就話：「同Herman（何哲圖）講，其實我哋公司都有好多後生仔同訓練班學員，Herman唔做我做啦。」<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190106/large/1546744844_638a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190106%2Flarge%2F1546744844_638a.jpg&h=9a445365&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n大台出動近60人，有市民好興奮咁睇明星，亦有市民皺眉話：「都唔識嘅！」<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190106/large/1546744845_896f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190106%2Flarge%2F1546744845_896f.jpg&h=c081e3a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMIRROR獲半百歌迷到場舉牌支持，並以姜濤歌迷最多。<br />\n</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190106/59110348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59110348&d=mSCPsj%2BCpXNT31el%2F4C9Ktr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d1a7d485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59110348&h=18170071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190106/59110348</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190106/59110081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59110081&d=mSCPsj%2BCpXNT31el%2F4C9Ktr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fdd33375\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59110081&h=267bd054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190106/59110081</a>"},{"pid":"a23dbc47e207209454830d5103312fca99969fad","tid":970792,"uid":29080,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"整隊星夢學園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a28106ca00c64eebf7343dcb6cf10c9a2c734a","tid":970792,"uid":40470,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"a23dbc47e207209454830d5103312fca99969fad","tid":970792,"uid":29080,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"整隊星夢學園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"Cctvb點整都有陣柒味"},{"pid":"64829b960d66eb45cf6ab2e4e92ff93692679f03","tid":970792,"uid":10757,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:49:31.000Z","msg":"炒左咁多人 有錢搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36134509aeedc90ef2c0dc9ca9543a78600a1d96","tid":970792,"uid":16676,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"何哲圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係佢地私相授受, 攪撚到香港娛樂圈咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f45382362bfe2d92e4bb710f8001bb2470508a5","tid":970792,"uid":42804,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"Mirror嘅組成已經係食韓流條水尾，無線仲想食mirror條水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"